00:28:57,100 --> 00:28:58,020
 i ići sad opet umeti?

520
00:28:58,020 --> 00:28:58,640
 Ne, drugi.

521
00:28:59,260 --> 00:29:00,320
 Ja naručujem autobus

522
00:29:00,320 --> 00:29:01,700
 i ja opet objavim datum,

523
00:29:01,700 --> 00:29:04,260
 prijavim mi se 14 ljudi.

524
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:06,240
 Datum polaska,

525
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:07,880
 ja sad sam na vagi,

526
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,100
 da li da ga otkažem ili ne?

527
00:29:09,100 --> 00:29:10,480
 Ja kajam, dobro, ništa.

528
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:12,280
 Tad sreća je bi da je posao,

529
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:13,420
 tad funkcionira super,

530
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:14,480
 ništa.

531
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,500
 Ja ne otkazujem,

532
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,140
 idemo mi,

533
00:29:16,140 --> 00:29:17,020
 sad 14 ljudi,

534
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:18,240
 ja plaćam sve troškove

535
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,000
 od autobusa,

536
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:19,740
 od svega živu.

537
00:29:21,020 --> 00:29:24,500
 prolazi sljedećih mjesec dana,

538
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:26,480
 ja organiziram drugi autobus.

539
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:28,000
 Na drugom autobusu,

540
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:29,220
 18 ljudi.

541
00:29:29,220 --> 00:29:29,860
 Ja kajam,

542
00:29:29,860 --> 00:29:30,580
 bože, pa naš,

543
00:29:30,580 --> 00:29:32,000
 ono, pa kojeg to smisla ima,

544
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:32,480
 ono,

545
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:34,260
 ali, ja ne osjećam,

546
00:29:34,260 --> 00:29:36,160
 osjećam da ne smijem pustiti.

547
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:39,160
 Dolazi treći autobus,

548
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,780
 20 ljudi.

549
00:29:40,780 --> 00:29:43,100
 Ja gledam one autobuse u Međuguru,

550
00:29:43,100 --> 00:29:43,720
 to je krcat,

551
00:29:43,720 --> 00:29:44,780
 ono, čovjek na čovjeku,

552
00:29:44,780 --> 00:29:46,120
 ovi moji ovako leže

553
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:49,400
 po cijelom autobusu.

554
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:50,020
 Ja gledam,

555
00:29:50,020 --> 00:29:51,900
 pa bože, pa kojeg to smisla ima?

556
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:53,540
 I onda se desi to.

557
00:29:53,540 --> 00:29:57,160
 Dakle, 14, 16, 20, 25, 30,

558
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:58,400
 trajalo je neko vrijeme

559
00:29:58,400 --> 00:30:00,620
 dok su taj autobus se nisu počeli puniti.

560
00:30:00,620 --> 00:30:01,820
 Na kraju,

561
00:30:01,820 --> 00:30:03,940
 ja sam bio u Međuguru sigurno

562
00:30:03,940 --> 00:30:05,460
 preko 100 puta

563
00:30:05,460 --> 00:30:07,020
 sa punim autobusima,

564
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,980
 hodočasnika

565
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:10,660
 i to je isto na nevjerovatan način

566
00:30:10,660 --> 00:30:13,160
 kako se to počelo širit

567
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:14,940
 između ljudi

568
00:30:14,940 --> 00:30:17,340
 koji su bili na tim hodočašćama

569
00:30:17,340 --> 00:30:18,660
 i koji su to jednostavno

570
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:19,780
 prenosili jednim drugima.

571
00:30:19,780 --> 00:30:20,280
 Međutim,

572
00:30:20,280 --> 00:30:22,740
 vrlo brzo mi je postalo jasno

573
00:30:22,740 --> 00:30:24,340
 i to me počelo smetati

574
00:30:24,340 --> 00:30:25,620
 da sam počeo primječivati

575
00:30:25,620 --> 00:30:26,900
 puno ljudi istih.

576
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:27,800
 Ono sam si mislio,

577
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:29,000
 bože, ako je moj poziv

578
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,140
 da dovodim ljude

579
00:30:30,140 --> 00:30:32,360
 u Međuguru,

580
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:32,980
 pa šta će on,

581
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:34,400
 ide već deset puta sa mnom,

582
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:36,840
 šta će on s menom

583
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:38,280
 stalno, pa već može ići sam,

584
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:39,380
 dakle da mu ja trebam uvijek

585
00:30:39,380 --> 00:30:40,480
 sluša istu priču,

586
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:42,860
 ono, nije mi to imalo smisla.

587
00:30:42,860 --> 00:30:44,760
 I onda nije prošlo dugo,

588
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:47,440
 dobio sam osjećaj od srca,

589
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:48,860
 počne organizirati maraton.

590
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:50,240
 Kaka maraton?

591
00:30:50,240 --> 00:30:53,380
 Maraton trčanje.

592
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:54,640
 Kako trčanje?

593
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:56,380
 I onda ja sada uđem u to

594
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:59,080
 i na kraju sa atletskim klubom Dinamo

