00:30:59,080 --> 00:30:59,820
 sam uspio

596
00:30:59,820 --> 00:31:01,940
 2007. i 2008.

597
00:31:01,940 --> 00:31:03,360
 organizirati maraton Mira,

598
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:05,020
 onako pravi službeni maraton.

599
00:31:05,020 --> 00:31:07,060
 Kako je to čudo?

600
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:09,100
 Mislim, to je čudo zbog toga

601
00:31:09,100 --> 00:31:10,680
 što nikad u maratonu nisam bio,

602
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:11,860
 nikad nisam organizirao

603
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:14,280
 nekakve takve sportske manifestacije.

604
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:15,360
 I samo je ovo za primjer

605
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:17,480
 da atletski savjes Bosne i Hercegovine,

606
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:19,540
 koji je zadužen za takve stvari,

607
00:31:19,540 --> 00:31:20,820
 koji bi on trebao biti

608
00:31:20,820 --> 00:31:24,260
 organizator nečega takvog.

609
00:31:24,260 --> 00:31:25,600
 Nije to uspio od rata.

610
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:26,560
 Ne znam da li je sad,

611
00:31:26,560 --> 00:31:28,280
 nakon 50 godina,

612
00:31:28,280 --> 00:31:29,760
 30 godina,

613
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:30,740
 da li je to uopće uspio

614
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:32,280
 izorganizirati.

615
00:31:32,280 --> 00:31:33,680
 Uglavnom,

616
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:34,940
 nakon tog maratona Mira

617
00:31:34,940 --> 00:31:35,760
 ja dobijam opet.

